name: Cowboy Cat #28 - Unique
description:
Reality is a mystery and everyone is mad. Am I the crazy one here? Always smiling even when I am sad. 

Cowboy Cats is a collection of 30 single edition cats in cowboy hats. Each pixel art is hand made, with love and attention to detail. The collectibles will include kittens, randoms, outlaws, a couple unique cats and a hairless sheriff, All pieces 1/1.
